snippet.title: Dino Ramen Express Steam Next Fest Trailer - Alpha Test Demo Out Now!
snippet.description:
Dino Ramen Express Alpha Test Demo is Out Now!

Download NOW on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2480100/Dino_Ramen_Express/

Dino Ramen Express is an indie game that blends restaurant simulation, fast-paced FPS action, and open-world exploration. Developed by a passionate two-person indie team, the game invites players to build a ramen empire while tackling unexpected challenges across vibrant, unpredictable worlds.
